    "Specifically, we treated the quarter before the launch of GitHub Copilot as the baseline and estimated the lead-lag model as follows:",
    "where, RelativeQuarterj is a vector of dummies that indicates Quarter j before and after the treatment took place.",
    "As per Autor (2003), the parallel trends assumption holds if all the coefficients (𝛼 $ %) are not statistically significant for relative quarters j prior to the treatment.",
